  "general_provisions": "This bill enacts provisions relating to sales of cigars and pipe tobacco.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>authorizes telephone, mail, internet, and other remote retail sales of a cigar or pipe tobacco;<hr><ltbullet>provides for the licensing, bonding, and taxation of cigar and pipe tobacco transactions between a remote seller and a consumer in the state;<hr><ltbullet>establishes a criminal penalty for failing to comply with the licensing, bonding, and tax collection requirements;<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes; and<hr><ltbullet>includes a coordination clause to align license terms and fees with other tobacco licenses as provided in S.B. 210, Nicotine Amendments.",
  "monies": "None",
